<h3>Import events for a new target</h3>

<p>
  To add or update events for target you first have to know the ID of target, and use Events importer.
</p>

<p>
  When adding new targets with events the good practice would be to first create targets in draft state.
  After the upload, you can download newly created targets filtering by draft state and created date.
  You will have Ids that you can use in Events CSV file. Eventable type must be set to "Target", Eventable Id - those
  would be downloaded ids, and you can add extra column "Eventable Title" with target name to know for which
  target you are creating a new event. Any extra column not mentioned in column descriptions will be ignored.
</p>

